        <div class="about-description">
            This project is a multipurpose website. It is 
            a web-based system to allow users to see live
            statistics of confirmed, active, recovered, and deceased
            people from Covid. The user can select any state of India
            and compare covid cases by region. The user can also
            see the nearest vaccination center available by entering the
            respective pin code. In addition to this, they can also 
            view current news related to medical and covid. Upon clicking the 
            link, the user gets redirected to the full article. This website
            also has a global tracker which helps the user to view and 
            compare covid cases of any country. The users can 
            also have the advantage of social media with this
            website as they can create posts and comment on other posts.
            The user can add pictures to their post as well as delete other
